	<p>Astro, Tailwind & Alpine kombineret i en fin, lille starter:-)</p>
	<p class="text-xl">Det bliver <span class="italic">flot</span> med Tailwind</p>
		<div class="pb-8" x-data="{open: false}">
			<p class="text-xl underline" x-on:click="open = ! open";>Og sejt!</p>
			<div x-show="open" x-transition><Button></Button></div>
		</div>
